Description: IOM1 Limitation of velocity at 10 V of AI11.The maximum velocity is limited to the setting inCTRL_v_max.The minimum velocity is internally limited to 100RPM.Setting can only be modified if power stage isdisabled.Modified settings become active the next time thepower stage is enabled.Available with firmware version ≥V01.06.
Parameter address via fieldbus: CANopen 304F:10hModbus 20256Profibus 20256CIP 179.1.16ModbusTCP 20256EtherCAT 304F:10hPROFINET 20256
